Parents know that bedtime can be a supreme struggle. But mealtime with kids is also often headache-inducing. It was only natural that Adam Mansbach would follow up his best-selling book for parents, Go the Fuck to Sleep, with a sequel called You Have to Fucking Eat. From picky eaters to epic food messes, the mealtime challenges are endless. Thankfully, parents can laugh about it. We’ve rounded up 52 comics about parents’ mealtime struggles. Keep scrolling for some all-too-familiar situations.